                            <comment id="14471450" author="tim_yates" created="Fri, 22 Jul 2011 02:20:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Had a quick test, and this seems to have been a bug in all versions&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(tested v1.8.0, v1.7.8, v1.7.0, and v1.6.3)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14471588" author="tim_yates" created="Fri, 22 Jul 2011 03:19:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Think this catches it, I believe &lt;tt&gt;cursor&lt;/tt&gt; in &lt;tt&gt;ObservableIterator&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;ObservableListIterator&lt;/tt&gt; needed initialising to &lt;tt&gt;-1&lt;/tt&gt; or &lt;tt&gt;index -1&lt;/tt&gt; respectively.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Added a couple of tests, to try and make sure I haven&apos;t broken anything...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
